WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:05.500
You discover an inflated vendor invoice that looks like a hidden kickback.

00:06.000 --> 00:09.500
When you question your manager about it, he leans in and whispers,

00:10.000 --> 00:18.000
'Some things are better left alone if you want to keep your promotion on track.' What do you do?